title: The Complete Collection of Commander Keen
description:
This is the Complete Collection of Commander Keen Games 1-6 and Keen Dreams.
The Games work best with DOSBox (not-included) or older machines. All of the
games are as they were when they were released to the public in 1990 and 1991.



I will seed the torrent for couple of weeks to see how it goes. If this becomes really popular I will continue seeding. This is my first torrent and I will try
